[Civil No. 823.] COUNTY OF PIMA, Appellant, v. CITY OF TUCSON, a Municipal Corporation, Appellee. • APPEAL from the District Court of the First Judicial District in and for the County of Pima. George R. Davis, Judge. Roseoe Dale, and Wright & Fleming, for Appellee. January 15, 1903.

No appearance for Appellant.

Affirmed on short transcript under paragraph 1583 of the Revised Statutes of Arizona, 1901.
